repository.name: eCupcakesFactoryOnContainers
repository.description: "eCupcakesFactoryOnContainers" is based on a simplified "Microservices" architecture and docker containers. Core intent of this reference application is to provide reference implementation for .Net developers to easily get started with containerized microservices using .Net Core and Kafka.
